Class FixedArray<E extends IPropertyValue<?>>

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.ddl.propertyvalues.FixedArray<E>

public class FixedArray<E extends IPropertyValue<?>>
extends java.lang.Object

Stores a fixed-length array of type <E> objects. This is a service class used in DDL.PropertyValues.FixedArrayPropertyValue.
